Package: twig
Title: For Streamlining Decision and Economic Evaluation Models using Grammar of Modeling
Version: 1.0.0.0
Author: Hawre Jalal [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hawre Jalal <hjalal@uottawa.ca>
Description: Provides tools for building decision and cost-effectiveness analyses models. It enables users to write these models in a concise way, simulate outcomes including probabilistic analyses efficiently using parallel processes, and produce results.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
